    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "But what about the people who argue that gun control makes things worse by leaving law-abiding citizens defenseless? Like, doesn't the right to self-defense basically contradict the idea of strict regulation? I feel like the \"safety\" argument ignores how criminals don't follow laws anyway.",
